{"type":null,"faqId":24725,"title":"自己安装的输入法无法使用，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.1.1.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 语言和输入法 &gt; 默认 &gt; 配置输入法”，点击或滑动自己安装的输入法后的开关，开启安装的输入法。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.1.1.2\"><a name=\"figd0e916\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86107\" style=\"width:3.7152777in;height:3.1493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.1.2.1\"></a><span>在任意需要输入文本的地方点击，开启屏幕键盘。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.1.3.1\"></a><span>滑动通知栏，打开通知面板。然后点击“选择输入法。”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e926\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86108\" style=\"width:1.7402778in;height:2.5583334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.1.4.1\"></a><span>勾选您安装的输入法即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.2\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86109\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":168,"faqType":"信息与电子邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8725","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Messaging-Emailing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104340000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"安装,输入法,无法使用,无效","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}